header.title: 250 Birthday party
header.intro: In June of 2022, a double celebration unfolded as I marked my 25th birthday alongside my mother's remarkable 50th milestone. The occasion called for a glamorous gold and black themed extravaganza, set against the backdrop of a stunning location in Harderwijk. Join me as I recount the unforgettable moments from our elegant and jubilant 250th birthday party. Let's immerse ourselves in the beauty and joy of this special celebration.

image.alt: Celebrating my 25th and my mothers 50th birthday together
